іNowhere is more loved than this treasured
place where joyous times are shared with
family, friends and all who stop to wonder al
the beauty surrounding them. Christine Kitchen."·
ҙPeace be with you. Love to all.
Hope for our children.
Cherished son, brother, uncle, friend.
Adventurer and actor.
At one with nature, his spirit flies free.
Wise John Glynn."ј
№Joseph Rifkind & Renee Rifkind
Walked and sat here every day, it was their special place.
They are remembered by their children:
Marion, Gabrielle and Charles
and their 10 grandchildren"ҫ
